**Reference**: N° 12504  
**Legal authority**: Chambre Disciplinaire Nationale de l'Ordre des Médecins  
**Date of decision**: 5 juillet 2016 (decision made public on 4 octobre 2016)  
**Place or address of decision**: 180 boulevard Haussmann, 75008 Paris  
**Context**: The document relates to a disciplinary hearing concerning Dr. Marie-Annick de C., who was accused by Mr. Bruno Eric F. of issuing an improperly drafted certificate while being no longer registered with the medical board. The hearing addressed the legality of Mr. F's complaint, which was originally deemed inadmissible by first-instance judges. The decision ultimately rejected Mr. F's appeal, affirming the prior dismissal of the complaint.
